    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国医疗器械采购展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-is-set-to-launch-china-probe-on-medical-device-procurement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将对中国的医疗设备采购展开调查，在对中国电动汽车补贴展开调查几个月后，欧盟可能会与北京方面出现新的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/eu-is-set-to-launch-china-probe-on-medical-device-procurement</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 08:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查驳回兴登堡指控后，Temenos 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/temenos-says-probe-finds-hindenburg-allegations-were-incorrect</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Temenos AG 表示，一项独立调查发现卖空者兴登堡研究公司对该公司的指控“不准确且具有误导性”，该公司股价自 2008 年以来涨幅最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/temenos-says-probe-finds-hindenburg-allegations-were-incorrect</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 06:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
